      <title>大都会人寿表示，2025 年商业房地产前景将改善</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-31/metlife-says-commercial-real-estate-outlook-will-improve-in-2025</link>
      <description><![CDATA[大都会人寿保险公司首席财务官 John McCallion 认为，在相关基金回报率提高和经济状况有利的背景下，2025 年商业房地产前景乐观。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-31/metlife-says-commercial-real-estate-outlook-will-improve-in-2025</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 31 Oct 2024 14:52:59 GMT</pubDate>
